<tr>
	<td><span class="topic">Why do video games on consoles need to be licensed?</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=17194">http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=17194</a></span></td>
